{
  "texts": [
    "Then the length of the fragments was obtained using pysam, a python module for reading BAM file.",
    "The SOB scores were calculated as previously described 16, and MAF from variant call format (VCF) was visualized with matplotlib, a python library for visualization 31.",
    "To avoid any preoccupation and evaluate DEEPOMICS FFPE and existing tools (MuTect filter, FFPolish, and SOBDetector) fairly, variant calls from every single vcf file were divided into a random train and a validation dataset at a ratio of 7 (train dataset):3 (validation dataset).",
    "For this, we used the train_test_split function of scikitlearn (https:// scikit-learn.",
    "org) with the \"random_state=42\" option 32."
  ]
}